    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieve their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping. Hemolysis RH index validated against FDA benchmark with GCI < 5% and output comparison within combined uncertainty bands. The primary hemolysis validation result (VR-hemolysis-mesh-convergence) was generated under model configuration ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which is the release candidate immediately preceding the production build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7. The patch delta between RC2 and the production release is limited to solver diagnostic logging output formatting with no changes to numerical algorithms, turbulence model coefficients, or hemolysis integration routines, as confirmed by vendor release notes. The validation results are assessed as directly applicable to the released model of record without re-execution. Credibility assessment supports Accepted decision for COU1 CPB hemolysis evaluation.",
